    "If you enable push notifications, future login or session refresh requests for %@ can be sent directly to this device — no need to scan a QR code or enter a pairing code again.\n\nThis is optional — Cookey works perfectly without notifications. You can change this later in Settings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If you enable push notifications, future login or session refresh requests for %@ can be sent directly to this device — no need to scan a QR code or enter a pairing code again.\n\nThis is optional — Cookey works perfectly without notifications. You can change this later in Settings."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "启用推送通知后，未来来自 %@ 的登录或会话刷新请求将直接发送到此设备，无需再次扫码或输入配对码。\n\n此功能为可选项，不开启通知也能正常使用 Cookey。你可以随时在设置中更改。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Inspect recent application logs for troubleshooting." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
